{"tid":1336794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逆權運動】因應下午遊行 港鐵提醒若人多港島綫或飛站","createTime":"2019-07-21T05:59:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T06:08:35.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"42ac64820f68a500b0d1c393d36d4cd4cb28c82e","tid":1336794,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:59:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190721/large/1563688396_444b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190721%2Flarge%2F1563688396_444b.jpg&h=8993ff2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民陣的遊行下午3時由維園起步，預料會有大量遊行人士前往灣仔一帶，而灣仔會展同時有書展進行，預料下午及傍晚時分灣仔一帶人流增多。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵指部分車站會因應情況，實施客流管理措施，港島綫列車或會在車站人太多時不停個別車站。港鐵預計天后、銅鑼灣、灣仔及金鐘一帶會有較多乘客，提醒市民預留充裕時間乘車。<br />\n<br />\n警方在社交網站指，下午及傍晚時分灣仔一帶人流會比平日增多，灣仔港鐵站部分出入口會實施人潮管制，呼籲前往書展的市民離開時在會展附近乘坐巴士或搭渡輪離開。警方呼籲市民應保持忍讓，並遵從相關廣播及現場警務人員的指示。"},{"pid":"45a7804824bf3256a3d7f7b0554b854371df3628","tid":1336794,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T06:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a30ba79fe83e0df47d7e51736f6965f782d5b5e3","tid":1336794,"uid":64345,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T06:02:06.000Z","msg":"去書展唔比係灣仔落車<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28cc3e6308e1e8831fd0c2fcdf5a4f3c58e4524","tid":1336794,"uid":245441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T06:04:28.000Z","msg":"直達西營盤？"},{"pid":"ef007e6bcd21cb277e800ce47b2e4e1164e6142e","tid":1336794,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T06:04:30.000Z","msg":"將全香港所有人困係灣仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n柒婆既鬼計係無可能成功 佢只能困港豬<br />\n<br />\n我地好易走去銅鑼灣 或者金鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031109b86188e84b8c63e56b5280d0cb67c920ae","tid":1336794,"uid":12171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T06:08:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/e0nvNFW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe0nvNFW.gif&h=32930245&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}